social_posts.post_text: Congratulations on a very classy honor, cast and crew of #marceltheshell, because we just won BEST ANIMATED FEATURE from @nbrfilm and that is like one of the ones you tell your mom about ❤️
Thank you to @newyorkermag for including me in this very very sparkly list. This recognition really means a lot to me byeeeeeee 😭😭😭😭

Thank you to #newyorkfilmcriticscircle for voting @marcelthemovie as this year’s BEST ANIMATED FILM!!! And thank you to @thombrowne for this heavenly ensemble, (& @mrmontyjackson @kirinstagram @rheannewhite for this whole look)
But mostly congrats and thanks to all of my friends here who did such beautiful work. And a big thanks to @deanfleischercamp @nickpaley @bettyholm for not kicking me off the text chain after I sent the last pic

Thanks to @nbrfilm for chosing @marcelthemovie as BEST ANIMATED FEATURE OF 2022! Turns out i felt very sensual in this @rasario gown and its huge perfect bow! Love you, @mrmontyjackson for dressing me up so well, @kirinstagram for sweetness and great makeup and @rheannewhite for wrangling my wild mane. Next up @goldenglobes, mom!
Found my dad on the carpet

Living a very happy life on planet earth. Thank you @criticschoice thank you @oliviertheyskens thank the whole crew and @deanfleischercamp and @marcelthemovie @a24  And makeup @kirinstagram @nikkiprovidence for hair and @mrmontyjackson for styyyyyle

Thank you so very much to our cast and crew and to the @theacademy for nodding their smiling gaze our way. ❤️

Appreciation post for my sweetest friend and husband @benshattuck_ who has sent me many texts and messages to cheer me on this week. I love him and he’s the best. (He also just took me out to a spaghetti and meatball dinner and that’s not a euphemism it’s just what was for dinner for me. Plus cocktails.)

Thank you to @thombrowne for my two perfect gowns, for putting my husband @benshattuck_ in such a gorgeous tux that he looked like James Bond, to @bettyholm and Dan Berger for holding hands and sticking out their tongues at the Oscars, and to @mrmontyjackson for saving the day. No one works harder than Monty and @kirinstagram who legit just had to call me to teach me how to make a reel. We didn’t win, but it actually feels like we did? So, that’s good news! Oh and @gismondi1754 thank you for adorning me with this breathtaking emerald and diamond embrace!
@thombrowne x @vanityfair x @benshattuck_ x what more could a person desire?

If you are looking for an excellent read, a gorgeous book, many laughs, please go ahead and buy this book. It is such a good one. @juliallangbein doled out delight. This is one of the ones that, even when you are not actively reading it, you feel its liveliness in your life, like knowing that your beloved has landed in the city. You can feel it’s existence even if you are not physically with it. It is a big heart-brain-turn-on and you know Im very attracted to that combo. Congrats, Jules. You’re a fucking genius, but we’ve been saying that since Y2K. LINK IN BIO TO BUY IT. Comes out 3/21❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️

While I’m at it: just in case you were wondering, this is my daughters very very favorite book. It is also one of my favorite books! @thyraheder is one of my very favorite, children’s book authors and illustrator’s, and I have a feeling that we will read this book until it totally disintegrates, and we have to buy it again. Even if you are not a child, this is a very nice book to have in your house. It’s via @abramskids and on sale now everywhere.

Sound on, pls. This is @kirinstagram. She is my friend and makeup artist. This is a video she sent me of  her listening to the applause at the end of the special I just filmed last night. This is a perfect example of what it looks like when a friend is proud of you. Kirin, you’ve been through it all with me. I will thank you and love you repeatedly and on purpose and forever.

My furry friends on @SesameStreet and I got together for this special song! We may feel happy. We may feel scared. But, no matter what the emotion, it’s important that we feel. Take a moment to think about what you’re feeling today! 💛 Catch me in #ElmosMindfulnessSpectacular on YouTube. Watch the full special in my link in bio. #WellnessWednesday #EmotionalWellBeing
Hi Madison! I am coming to you on 10/12 to talk with the brilliant @nerdfromthefuture about my book and all things creative! Come and see! Bring a question! I will try my best to answer it!

Heeeeeey I am doing a benefit for @semaponline on 12/16. I’ll be reading from LITTLE WEIRDS, plus new writing too! Link for tix in bio. Please join us and support our local network of farms and farmers!  This event is a fundraiser to benefit the Southeastern Massachusetts Agricultural Partnership, a nonprofit organization focused on expanding access to local food and promoting sustainable farming since 1998. Proceeds from this event will be put right to work supporting farmers in SE Massachusetts, preserving our beautiful agricultural landscapes and building an equitable and resilient regional food system.

DEAR LIVING PPL & GHOSTS TOO, I MADE A NEW STAND-UP SPECIAL AND ITS COMING OUT SOON! We all just want to be brave for love, right? Watch my new special ‘Jenny Slate: Seasoned Professional’, coming to @primevideo on February 23rd! 

Thank you to @gillianrobespierre for directing and @bettyholm for producing and generally getting my material to where it ended up. Thanks @a24 for supporting my work! I’m glad we did this! I’m glad you will see it soon!
